&lt;P&gt;Brilliant.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;You anti-pvp people really need to give it a rest.&amp;nbsp; Just once, next time there's a PvP thread, throw the rest of us a bone and try refraining from derailing the topic, please.&amp;nbsp; We get it....You aren't interested in PvP.&amp;nbsp; Why don't you demonstrate that disinterest in earnest by staying out of it.&amp;nbsp; You aren't going to play on a PvP server, so in the end, it really doesn't concern you.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Or here's a novel concept:&amp;nbsp; Why don't you demonstrate that class and overwhelming consideration for other players you claim doesn't exist on red servers but abounds on blue servers and just stay out of it?&amp;nbsp; I find it absurd that people can in one breath insist that there should be no pvp because pvpers only want to "ruin the fun" of others, while at the very same time demonstrating that very same callous disregard in an attempt to derail a meaningful discussion.&amp;nbsp; Far be it from bluebies to try to ruin the fun of others.&amp;nbsp; Please.&amp;nbsp; That very thing is right here in black and white and you people are just as guilty of it as anyone else.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;And to the PvP people who've been bickering with these idiots for the last 2 pages, congrats to you as well.&amp;nbsp; You do nothing but confirm what they have to say about PvP players with your stupid threats and antics.&amp;nbsp; And here's a little tip.....If you want a real discussion on PvP to take place, DISCUSS PvP.&amp;nbsp; Don't let them draw you off the subject into the absurd arguments that have nothing to do with PvP.&amp;nbsp; Several of us had a meaningful conversation about PvP going on, which at one point included a discussion of what ass-hats PvP players are supposed to be.....Then 3 pages later, a couple of you come here and demonstrate that very same ass-hatness.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Brilliant.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&#xD;
&lt;HR&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/BLOCKQUOTE&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;BR&gt;When a pro-pvper goes spouting off that he is going to intentionally grief blue players on the combine server, because he's a little whiny baby who didn't get his way, we have every right to say something about it.&amp;nbsp; These boards are free for everyone to post on.&amp;nbsp; Don't want us to post in PvP threads, countering the obnoxious attitudes of the PvPers, don't keep starting the same PvP threads. This is the Combine PvE server forums.&amp;nbsp; Yes, Kyth said you can post here, but&amp;nbsp;don't get the idea that that gives you the right to say we aren't allowed to voice our opinions on those threads.&amp;nbsp; The&amp;nbsp;Devs are certainly aware of your desire for a PvP progression server.&amp;nbsp; Our disagreement is not going to dissuade them unless they actually agree it isn't financially viable, or would promote a negative community.&amp;nbsp; And&amp;nbsp;based on the number of mod edits and&amp;nbsp;threads locked due to overzealous,&amp;nbsp;immature PvP posters, the aspect of a negative community should be ringing loud and clear to the Devs.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;As to your analogy of us ruining the fun of you all on this board, there is a difference between arguing on a board, and griefing/ganking/corpse camping people in the game.&amp;nbsp; How you can even compare the two is absurd.&lt;/P&gt;</description>
